There are a whole bunch of people fighting Obliteron. Iron Raptor was 
going to sacrifce herself but Prowl saved her. She wanted to calm 
Obliteron down but now Liono Prime is going to fire on him. Octociz 
sees that and is now firing on Liono even though They are both 
Maximals. As for the TM3 thing, Vulois found a TM3 driver that was 
created when Cheetor sabotaged Megatron's TM2 device in the real 
Beast Wars. Now Vulois, Soundwave and mayve Ramjet are planning to 
use it to start a new faction and win the Beast Wars.
